        The Alfa Laval MAB 103 Centrifuge is a solid-retaining (aka solid bowl; manual-clean), <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge/">disc-stack centrifuge</a> ideal for the continuous, three-phase separation of fuels, such as <a href="/diesel-centrifuge/">diesel</a>, <a href="/biodiesel-centrifuge/">biodiesel</a>, and turbine lube oil.
