  <p>
    The installation of the MAB-103 centrifuge in hazardous areas requires the centrifuge system to be specially designed and configured with an explosion-proof motor, direct-drive transmission (replace friction clutch), and classified field sensors.
  </p>
  <p>
    The control system upgrade includes a NEMA 7 electrical enclosure, cables, conduits, and glands suitable for the specific zone of the centrifuge installation.
  </p>
  <p>
    We configure our MAB-103 centrifuge similar to the Alfa Laval OCM-103-Ex configuration with explosion-proof ATEX Zone II for offshore applications. You can read more about our <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge-offshore-applications/">disc-stack centrifuges for offshore applications.</a>
  </p>

